    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_011_038_000008",
    "sentence": "約乃曰：「天下唯有文義棋書，卿一時將去，可謂不廉也。」",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_011_038_000009",
